\": 562, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"the tough Le Golf National\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know how else to put it - I really wanted it.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want our name up there.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our name\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want them to know that we are great athletes,\\\" a teary-eyed Pagdanganan told Olympic broadcaster Cignal.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\", \"score\": 0.9975239649146972, \"rank\": 0.002167464534995722, \"text\": \"Cignal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great athletes\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"a teary-eyed Pagdanganan\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And this is not just for golf.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have excelled at other sports and I think it's a great wake-up call for people back home that we can excel in sports.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"a great wake-up call\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So if you could just find someone to support, that would be great.\\\"\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1030, \"